  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by the time it was going on for months, he was the editor of the, of the But he printed it in another place, and we had Hungarian prints up on Wilson Avenue, just, just west of of Bathurst, a small Hungarian and so, where they typed and then set on paper.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he also had the printing there where he printed some kind of leaflets or invitations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, and at one day I was there reading, they're reading the proofs in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I came to something in-- in my paper, and he couldn't think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just looked up, to think, what-- how should I correct it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I look up, there was a, a doorway in between that editor room and the shop.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A man is standing there, and wide open eyes, wide open.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There and just looking at-- and when I looked up, and you know, when you look, what you call a glimpse with another person, you can't turn your head away right away, right away.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, he just looked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He got a shock, turned back, and back to the shop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by the time, by the time he got out through the back door, this is [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whoo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It came back so, so, so sudden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and, and-- and in-- and in, in peace demonstrations then, and so I remember seeing the guy with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were always there, the counter, there was Hungarian nationalist and Lithuanians and Polish and so against the peace movement.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Queens Park.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went on, on fights with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, the signs that we carry, and so and with the stick, bzz, bing, bang each other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we came out because we had, we had a real majority.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
